{"tid":1402902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"致唔敢上前勇武嘅你","createTime":"2019-08-03T17:13:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T18:39:54.000Z","uid":12670,"like":91,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"8b436138786f8c060963a988760a9b0039d8eecd","tid":1402902,"uid":12670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:13:48.000Z","msg":"由黃大仙一役可以知道<br />\n和理非嘅<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無裝份子</span></strong><br />\n雖然唔可以爭取到五大訴求<br />\n但至少可以保護前線 <br />\n用街坊身份屌狗<br />\n黃大仙街坊好嘢！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過前題係<br />\n前線義士做完要做嘅嘢<br />\n就好閃去第度<br />\n雖然今日好多義士被捉<br />\n但大家都唔想<br />\n我哋唔應該盲屌<br />\n<br />\n加上啲狗見到有裝嘅就發晒癲<br />\n相反面對無裝份子起碼放輕少少<br />\n所以剩低留畀街坊處理<br />\n<br />\n希望各地區Group好好發揮和理非力量<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不受傷 不被捕<br />\n前線安全 由我哋保護</span>"},{"pid":"072079afdba4fd76fbbec8c0ba79a2364e076238","tid":1402902,"uid":241244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:14:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不分化<br />\n明白大家唔同意見<br />\n呢篇野原意唔係反港獨<br />\n而係希望大家集中翻五大訴求</span></span><br />\n港獨？小心啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400357\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fd83c7a0b742252b535b88ad754b1d605399d3fe","tid":1402902,"uid":93998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:15:07.000Z","msg":"最好就拉撚晒班示威者 搞亂香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1402145\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1402145</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"37e886e90272c76fcba1bee56612d2915d509297","tid":1402902,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T17:16:20.000Z","msg":"同我推上去<br />\n<br />\n輿論戰都要同藍絲死過<br />\n 【都市擂台】對於有市民發起的「不合作運動」，你支持嗎？<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/poll/f83b2360-b41c-11e9-8d6b-b77be6568e98\" data-sr-url=\"http